System Energy Resources Inc, a unit ofMiddle South Utilities Inc, said it plans to file with theSecurities and Exchange Commission a request for authorizationto retire a number of outstanding first mortgage bonds.    It plans to buy back up to 300 mln dlrs of 16 pct firstmortgage bonds due 2000 and up to 100 mln dlrs of 15-3/8 pctmortgage bonds of 2000.    To refinance the redemptions, System Energy said it wouldask the SEC for approval to issue up to 300 mln dlrs of newfirst mortgage bonds. Reuter&#3;